121
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:25,321
Shell, like the unique
and beautiful thing you find in the sea.

122
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:29,568
I'll drop you at the bed and breakfast.

123
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:32,405
Alright. Thanks.

124
