150
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:36,125
Scrap merchant.

151
00:27:37,120 --> 00:27:39,521
- When will he be back?
- (Shell) I don't know.

152
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:53,006
- Is it just you and your dad here?
- Yeah.

153
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:58,370
- You live here all year round?
- Yeah.

154
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,642
(Clare) I bet the winters are cold.

155
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:06,726
We sometimes don't see a car for a week.
But I don't mind.

156
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:16,322
- How old are you'?
- 17.

157
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:19,805
(Clare) Do you go to school?

158
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:23,521
