201
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:18,449
<i>(starter button clicks)</i>

202
00:35:30,560 --> 00:35:32,244
<i>(door clanks shut)</i>

203
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:38,929
- What's wrong with it?
- Inlet pipe needs replacing.

204
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:41,970
- Can you do that?
- I'll cut a new piece in the morning.

205
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:49,484
At least cuddle me.

206
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,644
<i>(Shell)</i> I <i>love you.</i>

207
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:25,047
<i>(faint crackling)</i>

208
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:21,880
<i>_</i> Are YOU getting up?
- <i>(Pete)</i> Aye.

209
