247
00:43:11,760 --> 00:43:14,001
- They look really good.
- Really?

248
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:15,809
Really.

249
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,644
I can't wait to show my dad.

250
00:43:19,080 --> 00:43:21,651
